parameters.name: Collection
parameters.description:
The name of the collection.

>  You can call the [ListCollections](~~2401503~~) operation to query a list of collections.

parameters.name: DBInstanceId
parameters.description:
The instance ID.

>  You can call the [DescribeDBInstances](~~86911~~) operation to query the information about all AnalyticDB for PostgreSQL instances within a region, including instance IDs.

parameters.name: JobId
parameters.description: The ID of the vector data upload job. You can call the `UpsertCollectionDataAsync` operation to query the job ID.

parameters.name: Namespace
parameters.description:
The name of the namespace. Default value: public.

>  You can call the CreateNamespace operation to create a namespace and call the ListNamespaces operation to query a list of namespaces.

parameters.name: NamespacePassword
parameters.description:
The password of the namespace.

>  The value of this parameter is specified when you call the CreateNamespace operation.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the instance.

parameters.name: WorkspaceId
parameters.description: The ID of the workspace that consists of multiple AnalyticDB for PostgreSQL instances. You must specify one of the WorkspaceId and DBInstanceId parameters. If you specify both parameters, the WorkspaceId parameter takes effect.
